summary: Professional with more than ten years of planning, coordinating and executing services of audit of financial statements, limited assurance works and agreed procedures, guaranteeing fulfilment of the objectives; with the purpose of preparing and issuing the corresponding reports in accordance with International Standards on Auditing (ISA), International Standards on Assurance Engagements (ISAE), generally accepted accounting principles, current legislation and the PwC guidelines; with experience in the financial sector, mainly; in addition to other industries, such as: pharmaceutical, manufacturing, retail, transportation, services and non-profit organizations.
